  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multi-backend rendering: Vulkan (cross-platform) and DirectX 12 (Windows)",
    "High-performance Entity Component System (ECS) architecture",
    "Cross-platform SDL3 audio with 3D spatial sound support",
    "Integrated ImGui-based editor with scene inspector",
    "Smart dependency management via CMake FetchContent",
    "Asset management with JSON and binary (Base64+zstd) serialization",
    "Forward and Deferred render pipelines",
    "Android, Windows, Linux, and WebAssembly platform support",
    "Thread-safe cross-platform logging system",
    "Layered platform abstraction with native and SDL3 mode"
